> <OLD>
>
> "We have to move!!!" yelled Perceptor and both males took Nightshift and ran
> towards the exit. Perceptore lead the way

<NEW>

As they ran towards the exit they could clearly see that it was block!

Earth and stone had fallen down over the area the door had once been
and it smelled as if someone had set off some sort of explosion and
this was the result.

MEANWHILE OUTSIDE

TUCSON was making his way over to the coordinates that LORD ELDER had
sent him, and he could easily make out the city that had housed the
humans that had been reported on, however there was no sign of them
now. The village was empty.

The cave that NIGHTSHIFT, PERCEPTOR and WINDLORD was not so easy to
make out as there a recent cave-in was obscuring the exact location of
the door. However a few moments of searching would easily reveal it to
the seatching TUCSON.

OOC: The cave-in has been quite extensive. The whole outer cave has
been filled in. If you remember Nightshift and the others entered one
cave then found another that led down towards the ining area. It is
that whole first cave that has been filled in.

OOC: Also Airly I have sent you some private mail. Please get back to
me when you can.

(TAG)

- Preston
